OL,6,FMPs are also pressing ministers to set
OL,7,Fout details about a promise to provide
OL,8,Fa disability "premium" to the most
OL,9,Fseverely disabled, as ITV News Deputy
OL,10,FPolitical Editor Anushka Asthana
OL,11,Freports
OL,13,FPrime Minister Sir Keir Starmer is
OL,14,Fbeing advised to urgently pause the
OL,15,FGovernment's plans to cut disability
OL,16,Fand health benefits by Parliament's
OL,17,Fwork and pensions committee, ITV News
OL,18,Fcan reveal.
