OL,3,CMPs urge Starmer to pause disability
OL,4,Ccuts amid poverty fears
OL,6,FThe cross-party group, chaired by
OL,7,FLabour MP Debbie Abrahams, has
OL,8,Fexpedited the conclusions of a report
OL,9,Finto the reforms - and has said they
OL,10,Fshould not go ahead without a
OL,11,Fcomprehensive impact assessment.
OL,13,FThe politicians say that disabled
OL,14,Fpeople must also be consulted before
OL,15,FMPs are asked to vote on the reforms.
OL,17,FAfter hearing from a series of
OL,18,Fexperts, the group warns of possible
OL,19,Funintended consequences.
