OL,3,CMPs urge Starmer to pause disability
OL,4,Ccuts amid poverty fears
OL,6,FThe letter warns: "The legislative
OL,7,Fchanges might not incentivise work as
OL,8,Fthe Government hopes, but rather push
OL,9,Fpeople deeper into poverty, worsen
OL,10,Fhealth, especially in more deprived
OL,11,Fareas, and move people further away
OL,12,Ffrom the labour market."
OL,14,FAbrahams told ITV News that she
OL,15,Funderstood the financial strain facing
OL,16,Fthe Government, and the need to reform
OL,17,Fwelfare to support disabled people
OL,18,Finto work.
