OL,3,CMPs urge Starmer to pause disability
OL,4,Ccuts amid poverty fears
OL,6,FBut she also cited expert evidence
OL,7,Fthat cutting benefits could increase
OL,8,Fthe risk of suicides.
OL,10,FOn Personal Independence Payment (PIP)
OL,11,Fcuts the letter reads: "We urge the
OL,12,FGovernment to delay its plans to amend
OL,13,Fthe eligibility criteria for the daily
OL,14,Fliving component of PIP and engage
OL,15,Fdisabled people and their
OL,16,Forganisations in order to co-produce
OL,17,Fproposals for a new PIP, as part of
OL,18,Fthe PIP review.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
