OL,3,CMPs urge Starmer to pause disability
OL,4,Ccuts amid poverty fears
OL,6,F"Most importantly, we need to
OL,7,Fguarantee that those who need PIP will
OL,8,Fnot lose out. At that point, it should
OL,9,Fpublish and properly consult on its
OL,10,Fproposals more widely."
OL,12,FIt comes as Starmer hinted a
OL,13,Fgovernment U-turn on pensioner's
OL,14,Fwinter fuel payments on Wednesday,
OL,15,Fafter saying in the Commons he wants
OL,16,Fto "ensure more pensioners are
OL,17,Feligible".
