OL,3,CMPs urge Starmer to pause disability
OL,4,Ccuts amid poverty fears
OL,6,FIn the Government's Spring Statement
OL,7,Fon March 27, Chancellor Rachel Reeves
OL,8,Fannounced cuts to welfare, including
OL,9,Fchanges to PIP and universal credit,
OL,10,Falong with #500 million of cuts to
OL,11,Fincapacity benefit.
OL,13,FBacklash has been building amongst
OL,14,FLabour MPs over these reforms,
OL,15,Fspecifically over PIP - a benefit
OL,16,Fdesigned to help with the cost of
OL,17,Fdisability.
